#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:2
msgid "Build Guide for Contributors"
msgstr "贡献者构建指南"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:4
msgid "This page is the guide for contributors."
msgstr "本页面是供贡献者参考的指南。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:6
msgid ""
"This library uses GoogleTest for unit tests and Google Benchmark for finding "
"performance issues. Both dependencies will be automatically fetched by CMake "
"scripts if they are required."
msgstr ""
"本库使用 GoogleTest 进行单元测试，使用 Google Benchmark 来发现性能问题。如果"
"需要，这两个依赖项将由 CMake 脚本自动获取。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:10
msgid "CMake Options for Development"
msgstr "用于开发的 CMake 选项"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:16
msgid "Name"
msgstr "名称"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:19
msgid "``asbind_cxxstd``"
msgstr "``asbind_cxxstd``"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:20
msgid ""
"C++ standard version for building asbind20. Must be 20 at least. |br| This "
"can be set to a higher version like 23, |br| testing some advanced features "
"that are only available in newer standard."
msgstr ""
"构建 asbind20 的 C++ 标准版本。至少需要 20。|br| 可以设置为更高的版本（如 23），"
"|br| 以测试某些仅在较新标准中可用的高级特性。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:22
msgid "``asbind_build_test``"
msgstr "``asbind_build_test``"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:23
msgid "Build tests and enable ``ctest``."
msgstr "构建测试并启用 ``ctest``。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:24
msgid "``asbind_dev_warning_as_error``"
msgstr "``asbind_dev_warning_as_error``"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:25
msgid ""
"Enable warning-as-error during the development. |br| This option defaults to "
"``ON`` and only has effect when ``asbind_build_test`` is ``ON``."
msgstr ""
"在开发过程中启用将警告视为错误。|br| 此选项默认为 ``ON``，并且仅在 "
"``asbind_build_test`` 为 ``ON`` 时生效。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:27
msgid "``asbind_build_bench``"
msgstr "``asbind_build_bench``"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:28
msgid "Build benchmarks."
msgstr "构建基准测试。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:29
msgid "``asbind_prefer_system_gtest``"
msgstr "``asbind_prefer_system_gtest``"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:30
msgid ""
"Prefer system-installed GTest over fetching from GitHub. |br| This option "
"only has effect when ``asbind_build_test`` is ``ON``."
msgstr ""
"优先使用系统安装的 GTest，而非从 GitHub 获取。|br| 此选项仅在 "
"``asbind_build_test`` 为 ``ON`` 时生效。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:32
msgid "``asbind_prefer_system_bench``"
msgstr "``asbind_prefer_system_bench``"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:33
msgid ""
"Prefer system-installed Google Benchmark over fetching from GitHub. |br| "
"This option only has effect when ``asbind_build_bench`` is ``ON``."
msgstr ""
"优先使用系统安装的 Google Benchmark，而非从 GitHub 获取。|br| 此选项仅在 "
"``asbind_build_bench`` 为 ``ON`` 时生效。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:37
msgid "Generating Documentation Locally"
msgstr "本地生成文档"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:39
msgid ""
"Documentation is based on reStructuredText (.rst) files and Doxygen, then "
"generated by Sphinx. This is used by ReadtheDocs, but you can also generate "
"a local version for previewing modification to documents."
msgstr ""
"文档基于 reStructuredText (.rst) 文件和 Doxygen，然后由 Sphinx 生成。"
"ReadtheDocs 使用此方式，你也可以生成本地版本来预览对文档的修改。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:42
msgid ""
"Firstly, follow installation guide of your platform to install Doxygen, "
"Python and Sphinx. Then, use ``pip`` to install the remaining dependencies "
"of documentation."
msgstr ""
"首先，按照你平台的安装指南安装 Doxygen、Python 和 Sphinx。然后使用 ``pip`` 安"
"装文档的其余依赖项。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:49
msgid "Run the provided script to build the documentation:"
msgstr "运行提供的脚本来构建文档："

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:56
msgid ""
"The generated files are located in the ``build/sphinx-output`` directory, "
"you can activate a simple HTTP server in this directory. You can preview the "
"generated documentation in browser."
msgstr ""
"生成的文件位于 ``build/sphinx-output`` 目录中，你可以在此目录中启动一个简单的 "
"HTTP 服务器，然后在浏览器中预览生成的文档。"

#: ../../doc/contribute/full_build.rst:65
msgid ""
"Now you can access ``localhost:8080`` in your browser to read the documents."
msgstr "现在你可以在浏览器中访问 ``localhost:8080`` 来阅读文档。"

